# package_basic.algo.ct
# Bounded algorithm-form witness for Package token, psame, TokenPolicy,
# and two-step psame chain checks over the concrete fixture.
#
# Program:
#   Production i emits 1 followed by the 7-bit binary index i. When the
#   manifest runner executes exactly input_length steps, every consumed head
#   bit equal to 1 appends the certificate block for that input position.
#   The remaining tape is therefore the positional certificate of the input.
#
# Scope:
#   This covers Package inputs up to 128 bits, including the listed fixtures
#   and the small generated sweep in tests/test_package.c. The C harness
#   independently decodes the same stream and checks the concrete Pkg := BHist
#   and TokIntro := hsame semantics.
